== 音乐录影带 ==
单曲所随同的音乐录影带在2月5日拍摄与[[多伦多|多伦多]]的真混蛋餐厅（{{lang-en|''Real Jerk''}}）<ref>{{cite web|title=Drake, Rihanna spotted in Toronto shooting new video|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/toronto/drake-new-video-toronto-1.3436004|publisher=[[CBC_News|CBC News]]|accessdate=February 7, 2016|date=February 6, 2016|archive-date=2016-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160920143002/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/toronto/drake-new-video-toronto-1.3436004|dead-url=no}}</ref>。蕾哈娜其后通过她的[[推特|推特]]账户公布其首播于2016年2月22日，并通过[[YouTube|YouTube]]发行了部分影片片段<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HL1UzIK-flA|title=Rihanna - Work (Explicit) ft. Drake|publisher=YouTube|accessdate=February 22, 2016|archive-date=2017-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170204222512/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HL1UzIK-flA&app=desktop|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其一共有两个版本，第一个版本是由{{le|X导演|Director X}}导演<ref>{{cite web|title=Get a First Look at Rihanna and Drake’s ‘Work’ Video|url=http://www.rap-up.com/2016/02/06/rihanna-drake-work-video-preview/|work=[[Rap-Up|Rap-Up]]|accessdate=February 6, 2016|date=February 7, 2016|archive-date=2016-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160609081427/http://www.rap-up.com/2016/02/06/rihanna-drake-work-video-preview/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而第二个版本则由{{le|蒂姆·埃雷姆|Tim Erem}}导演<ref>{{cite web|last1=Bradley|first1=Laura|title=Watch Rihanna and Drake Dance It Out in Back-to-Back Videos for "Work"|url=http://www.slate.com/blogs/browbeat/2016/02/22/rihanna_and_drake_s_work_got_two_back_to_back_music_videos.html|website=[[Slate_(magazine)|Slate]]|accessdate=February 22, 2016|date=February 22, 2016|archive-date=2016-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160404065258/http://www.slate.com/blogs/browbeat/2016/02/22/rihanna_and_drake_s_work_got_two_back_to_back_music_videos.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其音乐录音带在17日内观看次数超过一亿而因此被vevo认证。其之后成为蕾哈娜被Vevo认证的第二十五个录影带，也是最多被认证的歌手。

第一个录影带展示了蕾哈娜与一群人在夜店里跳舞。其中有一些镜头蕾哈娜在镜子前跳舞，德瑞克在说唱而蕾哈娜还是在跳舞，还有一酒保将伏特加倒入玻璃杯中。

第二个录影带几乎是以一次性镜头通过，蕾哈娜与德瑞克在一间充满粉红霓虹灯的房间里。蕾哈娜穿着一件穿透的衣服，德瑞克则坐在背景的沙发上。

